entries.s_6: Kyoopid, one of our wisest Festival of Love sages, has arrived! He's somewhere in one of the cities where the Festival is being celebrated...Tyrena on Corellia, Kaadara on Naboo, or the Southern Lake Village on Endor. You should find him and honor the Festival of Love!
